definitions.definition: Situated in, designed to be used in, or carried on in the open air .
Pertaining to charity administered or received away from, or independently from, a workhouse or other institution.

main_definition: Situated in, designed to be used in, or carried on in the open air . [from 18th c.]
secondary_definitions: Pertaining to charity administered or received away from, or independently from, a workhouse or other institution. [from 19th c.]
